The '''[[BlasTech Industries/Legends|BlasTech Industries]] K-14 blaster''' was a compact [[Blaster pistol/Legends|blaster pistol]], typically worn in a [[Holster/Legends|holster]] on the wearer's hip. As [[Emperor's Hand/Legends|Emperor's Hand]], [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] used a K-14 as her usual sidearm, along with her [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] and other concealed holdout weapons.

